g.aria-label: bool check_password(const char* passwd, size_t len) { state_t state; switch (ENC(state)) { case 0x16fa64: state = (len != 5) ? 0x1b0f2a : 0x19842c; break; case 0x135044: state = (passwd[0] == 'O') ? 0x1512a5 : 0x1b9821; break; case 0xedf34: state = (passwd[1] == 'M') ? 0x16a09d : 0x114549; break; ... case 0x17f0d6: return true; case 0x1233c3: return false; } }
